keeping your personal information current and accurate is an essential part of maintaining your academic record.update your personal information via your mysjsu account. if updating via mysjsu not available, you need to submit personal information change request via online or submit pdf form [pdf]. see the table below for details:*see instructions how to edit your preferred name, address and phone number on page 5 [pdf]need to submit personal information change request via online or submit pdf form. see table below:either submitting the personal information change request via online or pdf form [pdf], you will be required to submit supporting documents to validate the change. these documents must be government-issued documents, such as a court order, drivers license, social security card, or passport.you may submit this form via email to records-regist@sjsu.edu, dropping off in-person at window r at student services center, or putting it in the dropbox by the student services center entrance san jose state university recognizes that members of our community may choose names other than their legal names to identify themselves. sjsu allows preferred names - as long as the name is not used to misrepresent or evade legal obligations. the university reserves the right to remove a preferred name if it is being used improperly.starting spring 2022, students may use a name their primary (legal) name on their diploma. students must follow the guide to add a diploma name in their mysjsu [pdf] by posted deadlines, otherwise the primary (legal) name will be used.you may contact the office of the registrar at registrar@sjsu.edu. phone:408-283-7500(select option 3)fax: 408-924-2077 email:general inquiries: registrar@sjsu.edu docusign forms submission: records-regist@sjsu.edu phone hours: mon - fri: 9:00 a.m. - 4:00 p.m.live chat hours: mon - fri: 10:30 a.m. - 11:30 a.m and 1:00 p.m. - 3:00 p.m.closed weekends and holidays student services center (ssc), window "r"(first floor of north garage, enter on 9th street)hours: mon.- thu: 8:15 a.m. - 4:45 p.m., fri: 9:00 - 4:30 ("" by appointment via qless) mailing address office of the registrar san jose state university one washington square san jose, ca 95192-0009